<p>Equivalent to:</p>
<div class=3D"highlight-python3 notranslate"><div class=3D"highlight" style=
=3D"position: relative;"><button class=3D"copybutton" type=3D"button" title=
=3D"Copy to clipboard">Copy</button><pre><span></span><span class=3D"k">def=
</span><span class=3D"w"> </span><span class=3D"nf">bit_count</span><span c=
lass=3D"p">(</span><span class=3D"bp">self</span><span class=3D"p">):</span=
>
    <span class=3D"k">return</span> <span class=3D"nb">bin</span><span clas=
s=3D"p">(</span><span class=3D"bp">self</span><span class=3D"p">)</span><sp=
an class=3D"o">.</span><span class=3D"n">count</span><span class=3D"p">(</s=
