xceptions.html#OverflowError" title=3D"OverflowError"><code class=3D"xref p=
y py-exc docutils literal notranslate"><span class=3D"pre">OverflowError</s=
pan></code></a> on infinities and a <a class=3D"reference internal" href=3D=
"https://docs.python.org/3/library/exceptions.html#ValueError" title=3D"Val=
ueError"><code class=3D"xref py py-exc docutils literal notranslate"><span =
class=3D"pre">ValueError</span></code></a> on
NaNs.</p>
