<p>What has happened is that <code class=3D"docutils literal notranslate"><=
span class=3D"pre">[[]]</span></code> is a one-element list containing an e=
mpty
list, so all three elements of <code class=3D"docutils literal notranslate"=
><span class=3D"pre">[[]]</span> <span class=3D"pre">*</span> <span class=
=3D"pre">3</span></code> are references to this single empty
list.  Modifying any of the elements of <code class=3D"docutils literal not=
ranslate"><span class=3D"pre">lists</span></code> modifies this single list=
.
You can create a list of different lists this way:</p>
<div class=3D"highlight-python3 notranslate"><div class=3D"highlight" style=
=3D"position: relative;"><button class=3D"copybutton" type=3D"button" title=
