n> <span class=3D"pre">+</span> <span class=3D"pre">n*k</span></code> such =
that <code class=3D"docutils literal notranslate"><span class=3D"pre">0</sp=
an> <span class=3D"pre">&lt;=3D</span> <span class=3D"pre">n</span> <span c=
lass=3D"pre">&lt;</span> <span class=3D"pre">(j-i)/k</span></code>.  In oth=
er words,
the indices are <code class=3D"docutils literal notranslate"><span class=3D=
"pre">i</span></code>, <code class=3D"docutils literal notranslate"><span c=
