<dd><p>Return a copy of the string where all tab characters are replaced by=
 one or
more spaces, depending on the current column and the given tab size.  Tab
positions occur every <em>tabsize</em> characters (default is 8, giving tab
positions at columns 0, 8, 16 and so on).  To expand the string, the curren=
t
column is set to zero and the string is examined character by character.  I=
f
the character is a tab (<code class=3D"docutils literal notranslate"><span =
class=3D"pre">\t</span></code>), one or more space characters are inserted
in the result until the current column is equal to the next tab position.
(The tab character itself is not copied.)  If the character is a newline
(<code class=3D"docutils literal notranslate"><span class=3D"pre">\n</span>=
</code>) or return (<code class=3D"docutils literal notranslate"><span clas=
s=3D"pre">\r</span></code>), it is copied and the current column is reset t=
o
zero.  Any other character is copied unchanged and the current column is
incremented by one regardless of how the character is represented when
printed. For example:</p>
<div class=3D"highlight-python3 notranslate"><div class=3D"highlight" style=
=3D"position: relative;"><button class=3D"copybutton" type=3D"button" title=
=3D"Copy to clipboard">Copy</button><pre><span></span><span class=3D"gp">&g=
t;&gt;&gt; </span><span class=3D"s1">'01</span><span class=3D"se">\t</span>=
<span class=3D"s1">012</span><span class=3D"se">\t</span><span class=3D"s1"=
>0123</span><span class=3D"se">\t</span><span class=3D"s1">01234'</span><sp=
an class=3D"o">.</span><span class=3D"n">expandtabs</span><span class=3D"p"=
>()</span>
<span class=3D"go">'01      012     0123    01234'</span>
<span class=3D"gp">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class=3D"s1">'01</span><span c=
lass=3D"se">\t</span><span class=3D"s1">012</span><span class=3D"se">\t</sp=
an><span class=3D"s1">0123</span><span class=3D"se">\t</span><span class=3D=
"s1">01234'</span><span class=3D"o">.</span><span class=3D"n">expandtabs</s=
pan><span class=3D"p">(</span><span class=3D"mi">4</span><span class=3D"p">=
)</span>
<span class=3D"go">'01  012 0123    01234'</span>
<span class=3D"gp">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class=3D"nb">print</span><span=
 class=3D"p">(</span><span class=3D"s1">'01</span><span class=3D"se">\t</sp=
an><span class=3D"s1">012</span><span class=3D"se">\n</span><span class=3D"=
s1">0123</span><span class=3D"se">\t</span><span class=3D"s1">01234'</span>=
<span class=3D"o">.</span><span class=3D"n">expandtabs</span><span class=3D=
"p">(</span><span class=3D"mi">4</span><span class=3D"p">))</span>
