<p><a class=3D"reference internal" href=3D"https://docs.python.org/3/librar=
y/keyword.html#keyword.iskeyword" title=3D"keyword.iskeyword"><code class=
=3D"xref py py-func docutils literal notranslate"><span class=3D"pre">keywo=
rd.iskeyword()</span></code></a> can be used to test whether string <code c=
lass=3D"docutils literal notranslate"><span class=3D"pre">s</span></code> i=
s a reserved
