=3D"xref py py-meth docutils literal notranslate"><span class=3D"pre">isdec=
imal()</span></code></a> and <a class=3D"reference internal" href=3D"https:=
//docs.python.org/3/library/stdtypes.html#str.isdigit" title=3D"str.isdigit=
