<dd><p>Return <code class=3D"docutils literal notranslate"><span class=3D"p=
re">True</span></code> if there are only whitespace characters in the strin=
g and there is
at least one character, <code class=3D"docutils literal notranslate"><span =
class=3D"pre">False</span></code> otherwise.</p>
<p>A character is <em>whitespace</em> if in the Unicode character database
