ary/unicodedata.html#module-unicodedata" title=3D"unicodedata: Access the U=
nicode Database."><code class=3D"xref py py-mod docutils literal notranslat=
e"><span class=3D"pre">unicodedata</span></code></a>), either its general c=
ategory is <code class=3D"docutils literal notranslate"><span class=3D"pre"=
>Zs</span></code>
(=E2=80=9CSeparator, space=E2=80=9D), or its bidirectional class is one of =
<code class=3D"docutils literal notranslate"><span class=3D"pre">WS</span><=
/code>,
<code class=3D"docutils literal notranslate"><span class=3D"pre">B</span></=
code>, or <code class=3D"docutils literal notranslate"><span class=3D"pre">=
S</span></code>.</p>
