><span class=3D"positional-only-separator o"><abbr title=3D"Positional-only=
 parameter separator (PEP 570)"><span class=3D"pre">/</span></abbr></span><=
/em><span class=3D"sig-paren">)</span><a class=3D"headerlink" href=3D"https=
://docs.python.org/3/library/stdtypes.html#str.join" title=3D"Link to this =
