brary/stdtypes.html#str.removeprefix" title=3D"str.removeprefix"><code clas=
s=3D"xref py py-meth docutils literal notranslate"><span class=3D"pre">str.=
removeprefix()</span></code></a> for a method that will remove a single pre=
fix
string rather than all of a set of characters.  For example:</p>
