g-paren">)</span><a class=3D"headerlink" href=3D"https://docs.python.org/3/=
library/stdtypes.html#dict" title=3D"Link to this definition">=C2=B6</a></d=
t>
<dt class=3D"sig sig-object py">
<em class=3D"property"><span class=3D"k"><span class=3D"pre">class</span></=
