separator (PEP 570)"><span class=3D"pre">/</span></abbr></span></em><span c=
lass=3D"sig-paren">)</span><a class=3D"headerlink" href=3D"https://docs.pyt=
hon.org/3/library/stdtypes.html#dict.pop" title=3D"Link to this definition"=
>=C2=B6</a></dt>
