> <span class=3D"pre">union_object)</span></span></dt>
<dd><p>Calls to <a class=3D"reference internal" href=3D"https://docs.python=
.org/3/library/functions.html#isinstance" title=3D"isinstance"><code class=
=3D"xref py py-func docutils literal notranslate"><span class=3D"pre">isins=
tance()</span></code></a> and <a class=3D"reference internal" href=3D"https=
