b">int</span> <span class=3D"o">|</span> <span class=3D"nb">list</span><spa=
n class=3D"p">[</span><span class=3D"nb">int</span><span class=3D"p">])</sp=
an>  <span class=3D"c1"># short-circuit evaluation</span>
