yping.html#typing.Union" title=3D"typing.Union"><code class=3D"xref py py-c=
lass docutils literal notranslate"><span class=3D"pre">typing.Union</span><=
/code></a> and used for <a class=3D"reference internal" href=3D"https://doc=
